txt.en: You discover some Ghâsh-hai who devote their time praying to the Ghâshghurm. Talath Úrui will only be safe once they are defeated.
Devoted Ghâsh-hai can be found in Talath Úrui, near the Ghâshghurm.\n\nYou should defeat any devoted Ghâsh-hai you encounter.
You have diminished the number of Ghâsh-hai in Talath Úrui, ensuring safer travels across the region.
